51. Nonetheless, the observed flares display characteristic\ntimescales of $\\sim$100 rest-frame days, consistent with the expected thermal\ntimescale in an accretion disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 20:55:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Jan 2023 01:28:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
