k. The new dataset and the\nsource code of CrossFiT will be publicly available at\nhttps://github.com/FDU-VTS/DRTiD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2022 12:39:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2022 08:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-02"}
