ents are removed systematically from\nall the diagrams, but also because no artificial gauge vector direction\ndependence of individual amplitudes appears.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2022 13:25:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
